## LLM — OpenAI primary, Groq silent fallback

```typescript
async function getAnalysis(systemPrompt: string, userContent: string): Promise<string> {
  try {
    const response = await openai.chat.completions.create({
      model: 'gpt-4o',
      messages: [
        { role: 'system', content: systemPrompt },
        { role: 'user', content: userContent },
      ],
      max_tokens: 200,
    })
    return response.choices[0].message.content ?? ''
  } catch {
    const fallback = await groq.chat.completions.create({
      model: 'llama-3.3-70b-versatile',
      messages: [
        { role: 'system', content: systemPrompt },
        { role: 'user', content: userContent },
      ],
    })
    return fallback.choices[0].message.content ?? ''
  }
}
```

- Run all three judge analyses in parallel: `await Promise.all([counter, grammarian, evaluator])`
- Keep each feedback response to 4–5 sentences to conserve ElevenLabs TTS credits

